data.description: This stunning 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom Otay Ranch home is move-in ready and nestled in a highly desirable neighborhood. It boasts a 2-car attached garage with additional parking, as well as a convenient bedroom and full bath on the first floor. Features include impressive high ceilings, elegant crown molding, new A/C and heating systems, updated duct work, recessed lighting, ceiling fans, a cozy gas fireplace and a designer kitchen with stainless steel double ovens, dishwasher, and microwave. The newer water heater and a beautifully re-plastered pool and spa with solar heater (within the last 5 years) add to the home's charm. The open and bright floor plan includes a separate dining room, a breakfast nook that flows seamlessly into the spacious family room and kitchen with center island. A large laundry room offers ample storage and an expansive upstairs loft provides extra living space. The grand primary suite boasts dual walk-in closets and vanities. The backyard is perfect for entertaining with a private pool/spa and a spacious patio area. Conveniently located near parks, shopping, restaurants and top rated schools. Truly a must see!
